<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Mary hicha Joseph ittatuklo kʋt ƲIT170</title>
<time_sig>11.11.11.11.</time_sig>
<aka>Away in a Manger</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Mary hicha Joseph ittatuklo kʋt
 Bethlehem tʋmaha ittonachi ma̱,
 wak i̱ chuka yo̱ ont anusachi̱ tuk.
 Yʋmmak o̱ Chisʋs at aialhpowa tuk.

[V2]
 Wak ʋhlheha't ʋlla nakni pisa ma̱,
 Mary't nalhilafa isht afohchi cha
 Chisʋs a̱ wak ai impa yo̱ bohli tuk.
 Chisʋs yut hashshuk shila anusi tuk

[C1]
   AMEN</lyrics>
<author>James R. Murray, Murray, James Ramsey (1841-1905), MacFarland, John T. (1851-1913)</author>
<hymn_number>170</hymn_number>
</song>